| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-2977 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 64c01c90-8ed4-53b6-893a-86ab8b2bf5ef"
